node.text:
Treat your friends with this ULTIMATE mini taco platter - who would you be happy to share this with? 🌮 

INGREDIENTS
* 	7 large tortilla wraps
* 	30g melted butter
Chicken jalapeno popper
* 	10 slices of bacon, diced
* 	4 chicken breasts, cooked
* 	2 jalapeños, finely chopped
* 	150g cream cheese
* 	100g sour cream
* 	100g cheddar
* 	1/2 tsp salt
* 	1/2 tsp pepper
Spicy philly cheesesteak
* 	2 rump steak, finely sliced
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	2 cloves garlic
* 	1 tsp ground coriander
* 	1 tsp ground cumin
* 	1/2 tsp onion powder
* 	1/2 tsp chilli powder
* 	1/2 tsp salt
* 	2 onions, sliced
* 	2 green peppers, sliced
* 	1/2 tsp pepper
Chipotle beef
* 	1 onion, diced
* 	1 red pepper, diced
* 	2 cloves of garlic, diced
* 	1 tsp cumin
* 	1 tsp coriander
* 	1 tsp smoked paprika 
* 	400g beef mince
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	3 tbsp chipotle paste
Guacamole
* 	1 red onion, finely diced
* 	2 limes, juice
* 	2 tomatoes, quartered and diced 
* 	3 ripe avocados
* 	1/2 tsp salt
* 	150g grated mozzarella
* 	Pickled red onions, to serve
* 	Coriander, to serve

500g chicken mince 
1 egg beaten
½ cup fresh breadcrumbs
½ cup finely grated parmesan cheese
2 tbsp chopped parsley 
2 cloves garlic, minced
Salt and pepper
 
Sliced ham
Cubed swiss cheese
 
2 tsp oil
40g butter
2 cloves garlic, minced
40g plain flour
2 cups chicken stock
1 cup heavy cream
1 tsp dijon mustard
400g penne pasta, cooked
1 cup grated cheddar cheese, divided
1 cup grated swiss cheese, divided
1 cup grated mozzarella, divided
Salt and pepper to taste
¼ cup pasta water 
 
Chopped parsley

Treat your friends with this ULTIMATE mini taco platter - who would you be happy to share this with? 🌮 

INGREDIENTS
* 	7 large tortilla wraps
* 	30g melted butter
Chicken jalapeno popper
* 	10 slices of bacon, diced
* 	4 chicken breasts, cooked
* 	2 jalapeños, finely chopped
* 	150g cream cheese
* 	100g sour cream
* 	100g cheddar
* 	1/2 tsp salt
* 	1/2 tsp pepper
Spicy philly cheesesteak
* 	2 rump steak, finely sliced
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	2 cloves garlic
* 	1 tsp ground coriander
* 	1 tsp ground cumin
* 	1/2 tsp onion powder
* 	1/2 tsp chilli powder
* 	1/2 tsp salt
* 	2 onions, sliced
* 	2 green peppers, sliced
* 	1/2 tsp pepper
Chipotle beef
* 	1 onion, diced
* 	1 red pepper, diced
* 	2 cloves of garlic, diced
* 	1 tsp cumin
* 	1 tsp coriander
* 	1 tsp smoked paprika 
* 	400g beef mince
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	3 tbsp chipotle paste
Guacamole
* 	1 red onion, finely diced
* 	2 limes, juice
* 	2 tomatoes, quartered and diced 
* 	3 ripe avocados
* 	1/2 tsp salt
* 	150g grated mozzarella
* 	Pickled red onions, to serve
* 	Coriander, to serve

node.text:
SANDWICH GOALS ’21 CHAMPION

HASAN SEMAY (@bighas___ ) - TURKEY 

Deft. Confident. Simple. Bold. Has’s sandwich moves are not to be messed with. Throughout the tournament Hasan has demonstrated his ability to resonate with our collective sandwich wants and needs; Crunch, ‘things that are wet’, contrast… light and shade… radical flavour… A deserved winner and European Sandwich Goals Champion ’21, as voted for by you, the audience. Congrats @bighas___ . Head to Big Has’s Youtube channel for more dench cooking.

Commiserations to our other finalist and runner up… the Sandwich King… @spasiadinkovski. Classy, tear-jerkingly stunning, fully delicious Balkan sandwiches are now something we clearly crave thanks to three absolutely show-stopping match entries from Spasia. With the Sandwich Goals World Cup looming, you haven’t seen the last of North Macedonia. Until then, thank you Spasia! Check out Spasia’s hustle Mystic Borëk to taste her food and keep your eyes peeled for her pop-ups in the Greater London area.

Many thanks to all of this year's competitors and our incredible SG photographer Caitlin Isola (@scaitboard). Finally, a special thank you to our SG21 commentary team, @clivetyldesley.

INGREDIENTS
500g chicken mince 
1 egg beaten
½ cup fresh breadcrumbs
½ cup finely grated parmesan cheese
2 tbsp chopped parsley 
2 cloves garlic, minced
Salt and pepper
 
Sliced ham
Cubed swiss cheese
 
2 tsp oil
40g butter
2 cloves garlic, minced
40g plain flour
2 cups chicken stock
1 cup heavy cream
1 tsp dijon mustard
400g penne pasta, cooked
1 cup grated cheddar cheese, divided
1 cup grated swiss cheese, divided
1 cup grated mozzarella, divided
Salt and pepper to taste
¼ cup pasta water 
 
Chopped parsley 

#pastabake #pastabakerecipes #pastabake #pastapasta #pastalover
